{"tid":1307823,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[連儂牆] 60歲呀叔比藍絲打到骨折 :(","createTime":"2019-07-11T17:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T01:18:09.000Z","uid":259753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"30985087653b2f4f3ae558b4207b6260edd3002d","tid":1307823,"uid":259753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:14:37.000Z","msg":"【守護大埔連儂牆街坊肱骨骨折】<br />\n<br />\n今晚8時許，有六旬街坊阻止「藍絲」破壞大埔墟連儂牆期間，被打至手臂骨折，涉事者逃之夭夭，受傷街坊需留院治理。<br />\n<br />\n根據熱血公民大埔運頭塘社區主任黃兆健提供的X光片，傷者左手肱骨上半部骨折，稍後要接受手術駁骨。<br />\n<br />\n相關報道：<br />\n阻止藍絲破壞大埔墟連儂牆　六旬街坊被打到手臂骨折<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-11-2019/54275\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F07-11-2019%2F54275&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjolFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=d136eb7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-11-2019/54275</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B9sSdMX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB9sSdMX.png&h=cb822855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2465407503522402?s=899990404&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F420361564693683%2Fposts%2F2465407503522402%3Fs%3D899990404%26sfns%3Dmo&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjolFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=980954f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2465407503522402?s=899990404&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/200954406608272/posts/2308653289171696?s=899990404&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F200954406608272%2Fposts%2F2308653289171696%3Fs%3D899990404%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjolFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=4edda3b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/200954406608272/posts/2308653289171696?s=899990404&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"